This is a personal productivity and learning management system called "Task Tracker" designed to help track skill development and goal achievement.

What it does:
ðŸŽ¯ Goals Management

Tracks learning and professional goals with deadlines, success metrics, and progress percentages
Categorizes goals by difficulty (Beginner/Intermediate/Advanced) and priority levels
Links goals to specific skills that need to be developed
ðŸ’¡ Skills Development

Manages a library of skills to learn or improve (tools, concepts, creative, analytical)
Tracks current proficiency levels from "Not Started" to "Mastered"
Sets desired skill levels and monitors progress through linked tasks
Stores learning resources and notes for each skill
âœ… Task Execution

Breaks down skills and goals into actionable tasks with checklists
Tracks task status, priorities, deadlines, and time estimates vs actual time spent
Calculates accuracy of time estimates to improve planning
Provides detailed descriptions and notes for each task

